      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers the perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals the expected minor stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary featuring supple leather upholstery that has been conditioned regularly to maintain its integrity. All onboard electronics, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict service schedule; it recently received a comprehensive inspection, an oil service, and a fresh set of all-season tires. It tracks straight, shifts smoothly, and provides a quiet, composed ride. Accompanied by a complete service log and two sets of keys, this car is ready for immediate enjoyment without any pending maintenance needs.",
